name: Original Concept #1
description: This is the original concept piece for "Cruisin'" Was thinking a lot about sunsets and clouds, the sound of wind, and the feeling of absolute freedom. This ship (currently referring to as Fortune) went through a bunch iterations and I settled on this wavy design cuz it makes my eyes happy. I wasn't thinking too much about line tension so the ropes holding the spinnaker have a curve to them, which was originally supposed to mimic the curves of the wind and clouds. @Slephy2 is ma twitter.
